  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  age &lt; 75 years with histologically proven adenocarcinoma of the colon or rectum

          -  no severe major organ dysfunction

          -  WHO performance status of 0 or 1

          -  Stage II (T3-4, N0, M0) or Stage III (T0-4, N1-2, M0) disease (according to the 1997
             revision of the International Union Against Cancer TNM staging system)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  age &gt;= 75

          -  severe major organ dysfunction

          -  WHO performance status of &gt;1

          -  Stage I or Stage IV
      </textblock>
